               <msContents>
                  <summary>A major work on religious obligations and moral duties, estracted from the author's Arabic work <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Iḥyā’ ‘Ulūm al-Dīn</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar">احياء علوم الدين</title>. Another more reliable copy of Kimiya-yi Sa'adat (for general particulars of the work see Persian MS. No. 231), being put together, apparently during the repair, in extreme misarrangement of chapters and folios. Also, many folios are missing. The following is the order of chapters and folios in this MS., in correspondence to the other four-volume- copy at JRUL, Persian MSS. 231-34.</summary>
